【Double Choc 🍫Brownie @berriliciouscreations 】
@berriliciouscreations Brownie made from quality Belgium chocolate and the finest French butter with toasted walnuts for extra crunch .
Best paired with cup of kopiO☕️!
Price is $25.00💥for a box of 9 Pcs Double Choc Brownie (Slightly bigger than 3cm by 3cm ) & packed in a unique gift box .
📣 The Pre-orders for the brownies will open at ⏰6pm this Friday 29 May .
Delivery🚚 will be on Sunday 💫31 MAY. 
So do follow their IG page @berriliciouscreations for their Next “ bakesale days” .
📣Delivery🚚islandwide at $10.00 , no min order required. 
Many thanks 🙏 Cynthia @berriliciouscreations for the arrangement!
